{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"beforeprint","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>当相关联的文档即将打印或预览以进行打印时，将触发 beforeprint 事件。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"基本信息","title":"基本信息","isH3":false,"content":"<dl>\n <dt id=\"specification\">Specification</dt>\n <dd><a class=\"external\" href=\"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/webappapis.html#printing\" rel=\" noopener\">HTML5</a></dd>\n <dt id=\"interface\">Interface</dt>\n <dd>Event</dd>\n <dt id=\"bubbles\">Bubbles</dt>\n <dd>No</dd>\n <dt id=\"cancelable\">Cancelable</dt>\n <dd>No</dd>\n <dt id=\"target\">Target</dt>\n <dd>DefaultView (<code>&lt;window&gt;</code>)</dd>\n <dt id=\"default_action\">Default Action</dt>\n <dd>None</dd>\n</dl>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"属性","title":"属性","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <thead>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"col\">属性</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">类型</th>\n   <th scope=\"col\">描述</th>\n  </tr>\n </thead>\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>target</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/EventTarget\"><code>EventTarget</code></a></td>\n   <td>事件目标 (DOM 树中的最顶层目标)</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>type</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/conflicting/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/String_6fa58bba0570d663099f0ae7ae8883ab\"><code>DOMString</code></a></td>\n   <td>时间类型</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>bubbles</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>事件是否冒泡</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <td><code>cancelable</code> <span title=\"该属性的值无法更改\" class=\"badge inline readonly\">只读 </span></td>\n   <td><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Global_Objects/Boolean\"><code>Boolean</code></a></td>\n   <td>事件是否可取消</td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"样例","title":"样例","isH3":false,"content":"<p>使用 <code>addEventListener()</code>：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">addEventListener</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'beforeprint'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Before print'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n\n<p>使用 <code>onbeforeprint</code> 事件监听属性：</p>\n\n<div class=\"code-example\"><pre class=\"brush: js notranslate\"><code>window<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function-variable function\">onbeforeprint</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token parameter\">event</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span> <span class=\"token operator\">=&gt;</span> <span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>\n  console<span class=\"token punctuation\">.</span><span class=\"token function\">log</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">(</span><span class=\"token string\">'Before print'</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">)</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span>\n<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>"}},{"type":"specifications","value":{"title":"规范","id":"规范","isH3":false,"specifications":[{"bcdSpecificationURL":"https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/indices.html#event-beforeprint","title":"HTML Standard"}],"query":"api.Window.beforeprint_event"}},{"type":"browser_compatibility","value":{"title":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性","isH3":false,"query":"api.Window.beforeprint_event","dataURL":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event/bcd.json"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p></p><p></p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相关事件","title":"相关事件","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/Events/afterprint\">afterprint</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"基本信息","id":"基本信息"},{"text":"属性","id":"属性"},{"text":"样例","id":"样例"},{"text":"规范","id":"规范"},{"text":"浏览器兼容性","id":"浏览器兼容性"},{"text":"相关事件","id":"相关事件"}],"summary":"当相关联的文档即将打印或预览以进行打印时，将触发 beforeprint 事件。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"Window: beforeprint event","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"beforeprint","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"Window: beforeprint イベント","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/api/window/beforeprint_event","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/api/window/beforeprint_event/index.html","last_commit_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/commit/5fe4ab11259b37914fab41914e84897fea47d143","filename":"index.html"},"parents":[{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web","title":"Web 开发技术"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API","title":"Web API 接口参考"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window","title":"Window"},{"uri":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/API/Window/beforeprint_event","title":"beforeprint"}],"pageTitle":"beforeprint - Web API 接口参考 | MDN","noIndexing":false}}